      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * Technical University of Munich</b>\n</p><p><b>Technical University of Munich</b>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Munich\">Munich</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Germany\">Germany</a>.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Technische_Universitaet_Muenchen-1.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Technische_Universitaet_Muenchen-1.jpg/330px-Technische_Universitaet_Muenchen-1.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"469\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Technische_Universitaet_Muenchen-1.jpg/500px-Technische_Universitaet_Muenchen-1.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/28/Technische_Universitaet_Muenchen-1.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Technische_Universitaet_Muenchen-1.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Main campus entrance at Gabelsbergerstraße, Munich <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Chess_Programs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Programs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Programs\">Chess Programs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Technical_University_of_Munich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Programs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Daja\" title=\"Daja\">Daja</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Siegfried_Jahn&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Siegfried Jahn (page does not exist)\">Siegfried Jahn</a> and <a href=\"/Ludwig_Zagler\" title=\"Ludwig Zagler\">Ludwig Zagler</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Elsa\" title=\"Elsa\">Elsa</a> by <a href=\"/Ludwig_Zagler\" title=\"Ludwig Zagler\">Ludwig Zagler</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Parwell\" title=\"Parwell\">Parwell</a> by <a href=\"/Elmar_Henne\" title=\"Elmar Henne\">Elmar Henne</a>, <a href=\"/Thomas_Nitsche\" title=\"Thomas Nitsche\">Thomas Nitsche</a> and <a href=\"/Wolfram_Wolff\" title=\"Wolfram Wolff\">Wolfram Wolff</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"People\">People</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Technical_University_of_Munich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: People\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#Bauer\" title=\"Mathematician\">Friedrich L. Bauer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Elmar_Henne\" title=\"Elmar Henne\">Elmar Henne</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Rudolf_Huber\" title=\"Rudolf Huber\">Rudolf Huber</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Marcus_Hutter\" title=\"Marcus Hutter\">Marcus Hutter</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Siegfried_Jahn&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Siegfried Jahn (page does not exist)\">Siegfried Jahn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Kramer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Stefan Kramer (page does not exist)\">Stefan Kramer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#HLangmaacks\" title=\"Mathematician\">Hans Langmaack</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Thomas_Nitsche\" title=\"Thomas Nitsche\">Thomas Nitsche</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#Samelson\" title=\"Mathematician\">Klaus Samelson</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/J%C3%BCrgen_Schmidhuber\" title=\"Jürgen Schmidhuber\">Jürgen Schmidhuber</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Thomas_Str%C3%B6hlein\" title=\"Thomas Ströhlein\">Thomas Ströhlein</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ludwig_Zagler\" title=\"Ludwig Zagler\">Ludwig Zagler</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Stefan_Zipproth\" title=\"Stefan Zipproth\">Stefan Zipproth</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Technical_University_of_Munich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#Bauer\" title=\"Mathematician\">Friedrich L. Bauer</a> (ed.), <a href=\"/Thomas_Str%C3%B6hlein\" title=\"Thomas Ströhlein\">Thomas Ströhlein</a> et al. (<b>2007</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.in.tum.de/die-fakultaet/geschichte/40-jahre-informatik-muenchen/\">40 Jahre Informatik in München: 1967 – 2007 Festschrift</a></i>. (German)</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <b>Langmaack's road to Munich computer science</b> (pp. 68,69)</dd>\n<dd> In the ninth grade in 1949 at Bismarck School <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elmshorn\">Elmshorn</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.bismarckschule-elmshorn.de/index.php?menuid=28&amp;reporeid=76\">Dr. Dr. hab. Hermann Athens</a> once hold a substitute lesson in mathematics, and he talked about electrical circuits and Boolean logic, and was convinced that one day circuits could play chess. At the same time our village policeman Woldach taught me to play chess. Woldach accounted Athens confidence for an impossible fantasy. Our chess nights now always ended in long discussions about the possibility and impossibility of mechanical chess playing. Mr. Athens was my first lesson in computer science education.</dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Technical_University_of_Munich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Technical_University_of_Munich\">Technical University of Munich from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tum.de/nc/en/homepage/\">The Entrepreneurial University - TUM</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.in.tum.de/en.html\">Faculty of Informatics</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leibniz-Rechenzentrum\">Leibniz-Rechenzentrum from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lrz-muenchen.de/english/index.html\">LRZ: Leibniz Supercomputing Centre</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www-hm.ma.tum.de/geschichte/node16.html\">Die Geschichte der Mathematik an der TU</a> by <a href=\"/Thomas_Str%C3%B6hlein\" title=\"Thomas Ströhlein\">Thomas Ströhlein</a> (German) </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Technical_University_of_Munich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Image by Rufus46, July 29, 2006, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Technical_University_of_Munich\">Technical University of Munich from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.idsia.ch/~juergen/cogbotlab.html\">COGBOTLAB: Cognitive Robotics AT TUM</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301082239\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.065 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.630 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 106/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:2164-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301082239 and revision id 8213\n -->\n"
